The '''Most Perfect Order of K'vin''' was a sect of the [[B'omarr Order/Legends|B'omarr Order]], and were a group of disembodied brains who worshiped their [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] leader, [[K'vin]]. They were situated on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The only definite distinguishing factor that separated the sect from the B'omarr was that [[Color/Legends|green]] nutrient fluid was used to maintain the disembodied brains while the B'omarr used a red fluid.<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|335|Most Perfect Order of K'vin}}</ref>

